Logistic Regression
A logistic regression model applies the sigmoid to the familiar linear regression model as shown below:

ğ‘“ğ°,ğ‘(ğ±(ğ‘–))=ğ‘”(ğ°â‹…ğ±(ğ‘–)+ğ‘)(2)
where

ğ‘”(ğ‘§)=11+ğ‘’âˆ’ğ‘§(3)
